}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 79-87.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   The sole extended comparison of the canto centers attention on the need for faith \softline
untroubled by reason.  These sheep, following and imitating their bellwether, are presented \softline
