}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 93.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   If we had not sensed the importance of humble acts committed by those 'not knowing \softline
why' in }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Purgatorio}{\plain \fs24 \f1  III.84, the fact that the souls, now described directly, repeat what had been \softline
done within the simile reinforces the importance of the point.  Denise Heilbronn ("Dante's Valley \softline
